    "Combine sequential day/week offsets into a single net day offset when order is irrelevant.",
    "Prefer direct day-based arithmetic over generating large candidate sets when equivalent."
  ],
  "error_handling": {
    "impossible": "If constraints are mutually exclusive or an nth weekday does not exist, report impossibility and specify which constraints conflict.",
