    {
      "id": "P2",
      "title": "Critical Checks Before Evaluation",
      "based_on_modules": [10],
      "steps": [
        "Parsing and precedence: verify that power binding vs unary minus is correct (e.g., -a^b parsed as -(a^b)).",
        "Associativity: confirm powers are right-associative; multiplication/division and addition/subtraction are left-associative.",
        "Domain/validity: pre-scan for potential division by zero candidates (e.g., denominators that could evaluate to 0). If roots/logs appear, confirm real vs complex handling.",
